The paper discusses the application of AI techniques in optical communication systems and networks, which involves topics related to network components, performance monitoring, nonlinearities, quality of transmission estimation, network planning, and operation. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). However, the paper also involves topics related to information theory (cs.IT), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), and computer vision (cs.CV).
